Net-SMS-2Way version 0.08
=========================

Hello. Thanks for downloading this module.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP Modules - tested with version 5.75 & higher
  Username/Password with http://bulksms.2way.co.za
  Credits with BulkSMS

WHAT'S NEW IN v0.08
- Added sample config file in the contrib directory
- Added email2sms.pl to contrib directory (A simple email-to-sms gateway)
  
WHAT'S NEW IN v0.07
- Added support for send_batch

WHAT'S NEW IN v0.06
- Added support for quote_sms 
- Fixed some of the documentation.

SUPPORT
- Bugs, comments & requests can be sent to lee@kode.co.za

